          "content": "Metadata-Version: 2.1\nName: thefuck\nVersion: 3.4\nSummary: Magnificent app which corrects your previous console command\nHome-page: https://github.com/nvbn/thefuck\nAuthor: Vladimir Iakovlev\nAuthor-email: nvbn.rm@gmail.com\nLicense: MIT\nRequires-Dist: psutil\nRequires-Dist: colorama\nRequires-Dist: six\nRequires-Dist: decorator\n",
          "sha256": "55e5b37552d0f211f5489bfcdb24edefc4c82a848226f903c713d25e012e5b60",
          "reason": "Replace the benchmark's editable VCS install with static distribution metadata without executing repository setup.py.",
